sourcesContent: import React,{useState} from "react"; import { TextField, Button, Box , Typography, Grid, Paper} from "@mui/material"; export default function Login() { const [isLoginMode, setIsLoginMode]=useState(true) const [showErrorEmail, setShowErrorEmail]=useState(false) const [showErrorPassword, setShowErrorPassword]=useState(false) const handleSubmit=(e)=>{ e.preventDefault() } const switchModeHandler=()=>{ setIsLoginMode(prev=>!prev) } return ( <> {isLoginMode?'LOG IN': 'SIGN UP'} {! isLoginMode && ( )} ) }
